  <description>
    <facet>
      <vocabularyID>LRE.expressionDescriptionFacetValues</vocabularyID>
      <value>main</value>
    </facet>
    <metadata>
      <schema>http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM</schema>
      <lom xsi:schemaLocation="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/lomv1.0/lomLoose.xsd" xmlns="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM">
        <general>
          <identifier>
            <catalog>oercommons.org</catalog>
            <entry>1770206919</entry>
          </identifier>
          <title>
            <string language="en">Document Analysis Worksheets</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Dokumentanalyse-Bogen</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Tableaux d'Analyse de Document</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Folhas Da Análise De Original</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Fogli di lavoro Di Analisi Di Documento</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Φύλλα εργασίας ανάλυσης εγγράφων</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Hojas de trabajo Del Análisis De Documento</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">are designed for students to use when analyzing photos, maps, cartoons, posters, artifacts, sound recordings, motion pictures, and written documents (memos, news articles, ads, patents, and others).</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Social Sciences</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">sind konzipiert, damit Kursteilnehmer verwenden, 
wenn man Fotos, Karten, Karikaturen, Plakate, Kunstprodukte, 
Tonaufnahmen, Bewegung Abbildungen und schriftliche Dokumente 
analysiert (Protokolle, Nachrichten Artikel, ADS, Patente und andere).</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">sont conçus pour que des étudiants utilisent en 
analysant des photos, des cartes, des dessins animés, des affiches, 
des objets façonnés, des enregistrements sonores, des films 
cinématographiques, et des documents écrits (notes, articles de 
nouvelles, ADS, brevets, et d'autres).</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">são projetados para que os estudantes usem-se ao 
analisar fotos, mapas, cartoons, posteres, artifacts, gravações 
sadias, retratos de movimento, e originais escritos (memorandos, 
artigos da notícia, ads, patentes, e outras).</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">sono destinati affinchè gli allievi usino quando 
analizzano le foto, i programmi, i fumetti, i manifesti, i manufatti, 
le registrazioni del suono, il cinema ed i documenti redatti (appunti,
articoli di notizie, ads, brevetti ed altri).</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">σχεδιάζεται για τους σπουδαστές για να χρησιμοποιήσει 
κατά την ανάλυση των φωτογραφιών, των χαρτών, των κινούμενων 
σχεδίων, των αφισών, των χειροποίητων αντικειμένων, των υγιών 
καταγραφών, των ταινιών, και των γραπτών εγγράφων (υπομνήματα, 
άρθρα ειδήσεων, αγγελίες, διπλώματα ευρεσιτεχνίας, και άλλα).</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">se diseñan para que a los estudiantes utilicen al
analizar las fotos, las correspondencias, las historietas, los 
carteles, los artefactos, las grabaciones de sonidos, las películas, 
y los documentos escritos (notas, artículos de las noticias, ads, 
patentes, y otras).</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Sozialwissenschaften</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Les Sciences Sociales</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Ciências Sociais</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Scienze Sociali</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Κοινωνικές επιστήμες</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Ciencias Sociales</string>
          </keyword>
        </general>

        </educational>

      </lom>
    </metadata>
  </description>
